Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you, traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Something drew you to my shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,something powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you have a keen eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alicorn Amulet\Nis one of the most mysterious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and powerful\Nof all the known magical charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid this is...\Nfar too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like that gift-wrapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 3 | Episode 5\NMagic Duel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed by GrayJeager\NFr.Jeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/GhxBronie\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared, little friends.\NTwilight is wonderful with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything happens to them, Twilight,\Nso help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, don't worry, Fluttershy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's magic has gotten a lot better\Nsince she accidentally
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,crushed me and Applejack\Nwith a giant snowball.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she's good with magic.\NTwilight's great with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I just don't want\Nmy little friends to be scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, look how scared they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise, Fluttershy,\Nnothing bad will happen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop!\NThey can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, that looks amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for now, little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can practice again later,\Nif Fluttershy says it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your magic has really improved\Nsince we came to Ponyville, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Princess Celestia's gonna love it!\N- Thanks, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be at my best when she arrives\Nwith the delegates from Saddle Arabia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she's trusting me\Nwith the entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Come quick!\NIt's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You beast! This shade of brown\Nshould only be used for accents!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Applejack. We've got\Nto get her into a nice, soothing pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,STAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's going on here?\N- Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't...\NTwilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Trixie!\N- What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You call that great and powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh! She's Rainbow Wobble, now!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good spell,\Noh Great and Powerful Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You two! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- What happened?\N- Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop picking on my friends, Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I\Nhave some unfinished business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic's gotten better\Nsince I was here last.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and you.\NA magic duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Winner stays,\Nloser leaves Ponyville forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!\NI'd never make a deal like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie, put him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?\NBecause you humiliated me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After you showed me up\Nwith that Ursa Minor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a laughingstock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere I went\NI was laughed at and ostracized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had to take a job on a rock farm\Njust to earn a living!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A rock farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're lucky a rock farm\Nwould take the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I want revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll just keep casting spells\N'til you agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?\NWhat do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Trixie.\NLet's duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lose,\NI won't set hoof in Ponyville again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you lose, you're the one\Nbanished from this one-horse town!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Snips, Snails, step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it,\Noh Great and P-P-Powerful Trixie ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:07:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,An age spell?\NBut, how could you do an age spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's only for\Nthe highest level unicorns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Twilight?\NGive up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight.\NYou can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie is the highest level unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it's time for you\Nto leave Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,FOREVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You proved your point,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can't possibly\Nexpect Twilight to leave Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay guys.\NI'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take care of each other.\NAnd keep an eye on Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something strange about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How could Trixie know\Nsuch advanced magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Spike, I can't get a message\Nto the Princess in Saddle Arabia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so who else do I know who understands\Nstrange and powerful magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tale of woe upsets me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you're dour,\Nit's an abuse of power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do, Zecora.\NI feel like I've abandoned my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't take her on horn-to-horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you train with me,\Nso good you'll be,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way\Nto make sure she won't stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll train me in magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was doing age spells,\Nweather spells, you name it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to magic,\Nit would be tragic
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,if somepony licked me,\Nespecially Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think I can beat her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, when do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!\NHurry up with my throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, how long do I have to wait\Nfor my apple sauce facial?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't doing nothin'\N'til you let Twilight come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll do it, just make it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie's cruel magic\Nis ruining Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony has to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No noise, no sound,\Nno din, no fuss,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,must interfere with your focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlearn what you have learned,\Nonly then can victory be earned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trixie is the highest level unicorn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is much,\Nmuch that I can teach,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but the answer you need\Nmay still be out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying my best, but...\NI can't stop thinking about Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something different\Nabout her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like she's gone\Nfrom high and mighty to mean and nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thinking needs a readjust.\NTotal concentration is a must.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This really doesn't seem\Nto be getting us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find anything that describes\Nthe kind of magic Trixie's doin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something!\NTwilight has every magic book there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I think I may have found something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's time for us\Nto consider our futures
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in this new Trixie-led Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, this sounds an awful lot like\NTrixie's magic--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants me to grow apples\Nwith no peels!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hay am\NI supposed to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, there's a picture here\Nof that necklace--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the Alicorn Amulet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and whoever wears it\Nis blessed with untold--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everypony, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This book has a picture\Nof Trixie's necklace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the Alicorn Amulet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and whoever wears it\Nis blessed with untold powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you read a little further,\Nyou'll see--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it provides great power,\Nit also corrupts the user!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but, um, you can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just\Ntake the Alicorn Amulet off her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a magical lock!\NTrixie's the only pony who can take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get\Nthis information to Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- She'll know what to do.\N- But, how--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If any of us try to leave,\NTrixie's magical forcefield will tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maybe we should--\N- I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to sneak past the forcefield\Nwould be impossible without help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know who's got the goods\Nto get into those woods!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fluttershy!\N-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Fluttershy?\NCan you handle the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'll crack under the pressure,\NI'll snap like a twig!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect! Fluttershy'll sneak out\Nof Ponyville and find Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I-- I--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know just the design\Nfor a dangerous mission outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony set off the magic forcefield,\Nand Trixie intends to punish them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But, wouldn't it be faster\Nif we had some... wheels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great and Powerful Trixie\Ndoesn't trust wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now pull faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling ya, Snips,\Nshe's getting weirder and weirder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You there!\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she so mean to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I miss the days\Nwhen she was just a fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh oh dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity's dangerous\Nmission outfit is ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'd better go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, you're right,\NI need to be brave and find Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the Everfree Forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is me being brave!\NI wanna be brave at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,locked in my closet,\Nwith my teddy bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\NI didn't recognize the Alicorn Amulet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The more she uses it,\Nthe more it will corrupt her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But how am I supposed\Nto beat that amulet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic's not good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle,\Nmuch work have you done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You learned all of my lessons,\Nall but one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If Trixie's tricks have you in a fix,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you must mix your magic\Nand use the six.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mix your magic, use the six...\Nmix your magic, use the six!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the six, that's it!\NZecora, you're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I need to get you back\Ninside Ponyville, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This better not be another false alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or the Great and Powerful Trixie will--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Twilight Sparkle?\NNot enjoying your exile?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about the Alicorn Amulet.\NI know you cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheated? Moi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And I thought\Nyou might wanna see
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,what a real magical amulet looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from beyond the Everfree Forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's way more powerful\Nthan your measly Alicorn Amulet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Nothing's more powerful\Nthan the Alicorn Amulet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And nopony's more powerful\Nthan the Great and Powerful Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to put your amulet\Nwhere your mouth is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How about another duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I?\NI already beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's up to you!\NBut I guess you'll never see
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the totally awesome magic\Nfrom beyond the Everfree Forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, you're on!\NA second duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with a simple age spell,\Nshall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Snips, Snails.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,An oldie, but a goodie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's see\Nwhat your little charm can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Applejack, Rarity?\NCould you help me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can do an age spell,\Nbig deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Duplication spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever seen one pony\Nplay ten instruments?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This-- just can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, one more.\NI can turn a mare into a stallion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Trixie, looks like my amulet\Nis more powerful than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With this amulet,\NI shall now rule
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,all of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness, my subjects,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,gaze upon an ever\Ngreater and powerfuler Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need\Nthat old Alicorn Amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!\NTha-that tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tickles?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That was supposed\Nto make you writhe in agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This amulet is defective!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Give mine back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. This is going back\Ninto hiding where it belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Trixie,\Nthe amulet around your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of Zecora's doorstops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But...\Nhow did you do those spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony can do those spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.\NNot even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zecora taught me so much about\Nmagic while I was in exile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She even taught me\Nwhen not to use it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:20:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My magic alone wasn't powerful enough\Nto take on the Alicorn Amulet head to head,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I needed to use\Na different kind of magic...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the magic of friendship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I also knew that the only pony
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who could get the amulet off\Nyour neck was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about\Nthe pony with the ten instruments?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not magic,\Nthat was just Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the least I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I treated you and your friends so horribly\Nwhen I was wearing that Alicorn Amulet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can forgive me, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sure.\N- Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think\Nthe Great and Apologetic Trixie
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is the most magnificent humble pony\Nyou have ever seen?
